title: Ep - 102 - ALEX AND TAYLOR FROM LAGUNA BEACH / ROSIE POPE
description:
Alex Murrel and Taylor Cole from Laguna Beach discuss being cast for the MTV show, the impact of fame at age 18, and who they still keep in touch with from the show. 


Rosie Pope from Bravo’s Pregnant in Heels talks about her craziest clients on the show, how reality television helped boost her brand, and how her family has grown since the show ended. 


Courtney and Jason Carrion from Married at First Sight Season 1 review the show’s season 8 finale. 


Shinan Govani, once dubbed “the go-to Canadian” by Page Six, reviews this week’s episode of Real Housewives of New York.
